{"tid":86863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白粉發功　陳浩天：3點打電話來　叫5點出去開會　哪有時間　唔係唔記得呀","createTime":"2017-01-19T11:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T18:18:14.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d76256109d27f098c470d5a71368afb3bc8a77ac","tid":86863,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hotin.chan.9277/posts/10155651741245130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhotin.chan.9277%2Fposts%2F10155651741245130&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=6768b4ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hotin.chan.9277/posts/10155651741245130</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Chan Ho Tin<br />\n<br />\n我係話3點打電話黎，叫我地5點出去開會，邊就得到時間，唔得閒冇去，唔係唔記得左去呀......<br />\n//陳浩天又稱，該黨發言人周浩輝以個人名義於去年11月8日競投維園年宵攤位，至前日下午則接獲食環署電話，要求周與署方人員會面，講解銷售規則，但該黨人士善忘未有出席，//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李瑞欣 邊個傳媒阿<br />\n<br />\n向玥琪 <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170119/mobile/bkn-20170119121939952-0119_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170119%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170119121939952-0119_00822_001.html&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d004dec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170119/mobile/bkn-20170119121939952-0119_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n祖記 你地報館班伙計點樣拉橫節曲，你地都冇得返香港架喇，收手啦<br />\n<br />\nChung Yan Leung 白粉<br />\n<br />\nCharlie Lok 賣過百份<br />\n<br />\nWing-Fung Lau 接受傳媒訪問 錄音好重要！<br />\n<br />\nWat Yee Wan 隨時都要準備錄音<br />\n<br />\n球三 屌吖，東方又老作新聞 FAKE NEWS<br />\n<br />\nPhoenix Un 天哥，謝澄清<br />\n<br />\nHelen Ng 被善忘的堡主XD<br />\n<br />\nRosly Mok D貨放上網賣得唔得架<br />\n<br />\nMuk Lee Lam 你係要澄清就最好正式啲啦！就咁放段出處不明嘅文字出嚟鬼知邊個屈你哋咩~ Zzzzz<br />\n<br />\n李政熙 翠翠不要哭<br />\n<br />\n王安石 仆街港共政府"},{"pid":"c5c2c7321e067f2b3e3d60e700f496992a0c903a","tid":86863,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"